9.1 – Gravitational potential from the foam field
phi_g = α_g * M / r
Scalar foam contribution from each mass (line 106).


9.3 – Modified Poisson equation
Superposition of all phi_g
We simply add the potentials → linear Poisson solution for the undisturbed case.


4.3 – Force‑balance (EM radiation pressure)
phi_em = β_EM * P / r²
Added only for the Sun (line 115).


